{"tid":624251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺香港人啲屋另捨霉霉爛爛、成個貧民窟咁","createTime":"2018-04-10T16:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T02:58:41.000Z","uid":143915,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"946737326075cfc4dbe78ba0d34e535f2f5bf9d9","tid":624251,"uid":143915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"次次睇YouTube ，我一睇個thumbnail就知嗰個YouTuber 係香港人，因為個背景永遠都爛溶溶、又細又霉又舊又多雜物，成間屋核核突突、毫無美感、極度簡陋，成個slum咁。仲要香港嘅爛屋YouTuber 佔嘅並唔係少數。<br />\n<br />\n經典例子，薑檸樂 :<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/001651_6edc8aadd034092f207a3bee5877d6f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F001651_6edc8aadd034092f207a3bee5877d6f5.png&h=07ae0288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉，窮都算，但你咪係咁show你間寒酸屋出嚟啦！其他國家嘅人唔知真係以為個個香港人都住撚埋呢啲閪屋㗎！"},{"pid":"0d7bdc0a886d07705e825dd991b0964f5bd00bd4","tid":624251,"uid":142604,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"唔好諗多咗 冇鬼會睇香港啲片"},{"pid":"4cba4d5b9805c455b1014d7f1ea312c43f1593e0","tid":624251,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:30:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a19f9a19a772e07cc4d01ed95583e611d6a24630","tid":624251,"uid":10692,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:30:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50866fb6c1cd0ef9d0bc86296b9efdd08b668a13","tid":624251,"uid":139676,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:32:50.000Z","msg":"應該靚過你屋企"},{"pid":"152485866137bbdb372f473dfff0a4873d80b3a5","tid":624251,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50866fb6c1cd0ef9d0bc86296b9efdd08b668a13","tid":624251,"uid":139676,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T23:32:50.000Z","msg":"應該靚過你屋企"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"咁都有得串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />